headline: What Are Wall Street Analysts' Target Price for Fifth Third Bancorp Stock?
summary: Fifth Third Bancorp has lagged behind the broader market over the past year. But analysts remain optimistic about the stock’s prospects, with price targets suggesting notable double-digit upside potential.

headline: Davis Financial Fund 2025 Semi-Annual Review
summary: Davis Financial Fund returned +13.77% in the first half of 2025, exceeding the performance of the S&P Financials Index which returned +9.23%, and the S&P 500 Index, which returned +6.20%.
